  "detailed_description": "MIYAMOTO is a single player card game with a miniature board.<br>Game art is simple and oriental world with Samurai.<br>Open the box of the board game and you will be dive into a world of miniatures!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=636 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The important tactics is\"when\" and \"where\" and \"which\" play your card.<br>Random deck on each battles will not promise their results, It's up to your tactics.<br>Collect unique heroes and defeat MIYAMOTO.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>MIYAMOTO S includes the extended content \"Shiba Inu\". <br>New units including \"Shiba Inu\" have been added.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=700 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
